    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion is softening, add your <strong>linguine</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>linguine</strong> for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain the<strong> linguine</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/684.-step2-x200.jpg",
