            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong> and slice your<strong> chestnut mushrooms</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your<strong> parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can’t handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>Dijon mustard </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Cut your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> into bite-sized pieces and add to the bowl, then mix well and set aside – this is your<strong> smoky chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
