    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms have started to soften, add the<strong> smoky chicken </strong>to the pan</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>parsley</strong> (save the rest for garnish!)</p><p>Cook for a further 3-4 min or until the chicken is beginning to brown</p>",
      "order": 5,
